Game Concepts:

RPG style exploration game using a ship that travels over and through planet surfaces and caves, 
searching for the lost relic, fighting hordes of alien enemies along the way.

-Non-linear style game play with multiple worlds
-Interact with NPC's in world which can provide missions of various difficulties
-Hostile and non-hostile worlds
-Ship will fly continuously and special exploration pod can go through caves,
however it has less armor and weapon damage, and can run out of fuel, unless
you can find fuel pods

Player Concepts:

-Level up to attain special skills (accuracy, hull reinforcement)
-Upgrade weapons and ship with materials refined from destroyed enemies,
however, they can only be built via hangar on a non-hostile world

